			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character / Hold to run:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Low attack:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Special attack:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Medium attack:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; High attack:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or L2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Guard:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 or R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Evade:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 or R2 Button (hold) + D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Roll:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad (twice) + R1 or R2 (hold)</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Crouch:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 or R2 Button (hold</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
        &nbsp;</td>
